UrlTextBoxPlaceholder.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Placeholder text for the URL text box in Mobile Preview Tool.
UrlTextBoxPlaceholder.value: Enter a URL to view in Mobile Preview Tool.

ScreenReaderMobilePreviewEntered.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Screen reader alert for when the user enters Mobile Preview Tool.
ScreenReaderMobilePreviewEntered.value: You have entered the Mobile Preview Tool. If you want to preview a different page, enter the URL in URL text field. To close the tool and go back to Workbench, press Escape.

ScreenReaderDevicePickerEntered.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Screen reader alert for when the user enters the device selector in Mobile Preview Tool.
ScreenReaderDevicePickerEntered.value: Use left and right arrow keys to choose a device to change the preview screen size.

ScreenReaderDevicePickerSelectionChanged.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Screen reader alert for when the user selects a new item in the device selector in Mobile Preview Tool.
ScreenReaderDevicePickerSelectionChanged.value: Press Enter to choose this device.

Width.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The width of the mobile device shown on screen.

Height.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The height of the mobile device shown on screen.
